product_name: Mario BadescuFacial Spray with Aloe, Herbs and Rosewater
summary: SummaryMario Badescu's Facial Spray with Aloe, Herbs and Rosewater is a cult-favorite face mist that helps revive dehydrated skin with a dewy glow anytime, anywhere. A floral infusion of Aloe, Rose, and Gardenia boosts the complexion - leaving skin radiant and re-energized.
details: DetailsBenefitsCult-favorite, multi-purpose mistClassic Rose fragranceRevives dehydrated skin with a healthy, dewy glowHelps boost skin's clarity with clarifying Thyme ExtractReveals radiant, re-energized skinItem 2504798How To UseMist onto face, neck, or hair as needed. Use it to infuse more hydration before or after applying moisturizer, as a pick-me-up on the go, or post-makeup application to give skin a dewy finish. If product gets into eyes, rinse well with water.#MBSkinTip: Mario Badescu Facial Sprays are meant to multi-task! Use it to before moisturizer to boost hydration, to dampen makeup brushes and sponges, as a final step after makeup application to give your look a dewy finish, and to refresh your face (and mood!) throughout the day.IngredientsAqua (Water, Eau), Propylene Glycol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Rosa Canina Extract, Thymus Vulgaris (Thyme) Leaf Extract, Fucus Vesiculosus (Bladderwrack) Extract, Gardenia Florida Fruit Extract, Caprylyl Glycol, Hexylene Glycol, Polysorbate 20, Parfum (Fragrance), Phenoxyethanol, Sodium Chloride, Citronellol, Geraniol, CI 17200 (Red 33), CI 42090 (Blue 1)Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Mist onto face, neck, or hair as needed. Use it to infuse more hydration before or after applying moisturizer, as a pick-me-up on the go, or post-makeup application to give skin a dewy finish. If product gets into eyes, rinse well with water.#MBSkinTip: Mario Badescu Facial Sprays are meant to multi-task! Use it to before moisturizer to boost hydration, to dampen makeup brushes and sponges, as a final step after makeup application to give your look a dewy finish, and to refresh your face (and mood!) throughout the day.

reviews.headline: I LOVE this!!!
reviews.comments: This product great for a moisturizer and a fresh feeling to your skin. Very refreshing and smells nice. Will be buying again!

reviews.headline: DON'T BUY
reviews.comments: Tell me why a hydrating face spray needs yellow 5 and red 40??? Like huhhhh? Awful ingredients. Literally just water, perfume and chemicals, and it will more than likely break your face out.

reviews.headline: I would buy this product again and again
reviews.comments: It moisturizes my skin very well, and makes it look super glowy

reviews.headline: Mario never disappoints
reviews.comments: This spray always leaves my face refreshed and ready to go! It is a really great value for your money, and good for sensitive skin. Plus, it smells super nice!

reviews.headline: It's ok
reviews.comments: Fabulous ingredients however it contains blue and red die! There's never a reason to put die in a facial product! Come on Mario.

reviews.comments: I loved the original one, but then the ingredients changed! This new formula has harmful ingredients in it, and I have very sensitive skin. When I sprayed it, my skin started to burn and turn red. Would not recommend for sensitive skin like me.

reviews.headline: best setting spray
reviews.comments: literally my go to spray. better than most high ends in my opinion. leaves your skin looking so healthy and glowy!!

reviews.headline: This is a great product
reviews.comments: Very refreshing and great for your morning skincare. I would recommend doing before moisturizer, but you can also do it after (I like doing this at night wit the lavender one). This can also be used as a setting spray, but I don't typically wear makeup, so I don't know how well it works for this.

media.caption: Looks so beautiful and natural

faceoff_positive.comments:
I absolutely love this spray! I have really difficult skin: dry patches, unsightly bumps, oily t-zone, acne, and dark spots galore. This spray has bladderwrack, which is a type of seaweed that is known for its anti-aging, dark spot reducing, and detoxifying properties. Gardenia helps moisture retention and reduce redness. Aloe soothes and calms irritated skin. The spray is slightly rose-scented, not from a synthetic fragrance but from natural rose extract. So if your skin gets irritated by perfume and fragrancy products, as mine does, this spray should be okay for your skin! Rose extract is also good for brightening and firming skin. 

I find that this spray sets makeup well and is a good mid-day moisturizer for my dry patch flareups. I also spray it on before moisturizing at night for those extra dry days. 

Mario Badescu's products have helped me so much; I am forever loyal to this brand. Consistent and simple packaging that doesn't hike up prices and high quality, natural ingredients is why I stick to this brand.
faceoff_positive.headline: Holy Grail Spray

faceoff_negative.comments:
VERY disappointed with the change in ingredients!!! I loved the original spray and had just run out so i purchased a new one. I was very annoyed at how different it was from the old one once i sprayed it. I saved my old bottle, compared, and noticed the ingredients are not the same! The ingredients listed on ultas website ARE NOT updated, BEWARE IF YOU ARE SHOPPING ONLINE!
--compare to ingredients listed on site--
ACTUAL INGREDIENTS:
Aqua (water), propylene glycol, aloe leaf juice, fucus vesiculosus extract, gardenia florida fruit extract, polysorbate 20, caprylyl glycol, hexylene glycol, parfum (fragrance), phenoxyethanol, sodium chloride, Cl 17200 (Red 33), Cl 42090 (blue)

NO ROSEWATER AT ALL??!! Yet on the front of the bottle it says it has rosewater? The smell is different as well! 
I'd also like to add that they changed the spray nozzle  which i hate! Sprays way too much product!
Sadly, this WAS a holy grail item. I will not be repurchasing!
faceoff_negative.headline: INGREDIENTS CHANGED!!!
